OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FTaylor said it was "highly alarming"
OL,8,Fthat the police and prison service
OL,9,Fhave "in effect ceded the airspace
OL,10,Fabove two high-security prisons to
OL,11,Forganised crime gangs which are able
OL,12,Fto deliver contraband to jails holding
OL,13,Fextremely dangerous prisoners",
OL,14,Fincluding some who have been
OL,15,Fdesignated as high-risk category A.
OL,17,F"The safety of staff, prisoners and
OL,18,Fultimately that of the public is
OL,19,Fseriously compromised by the failure
OL,20,Fto tackle what has become a threat to
OL,21,Fnational security.
