OL,4,C'national security threat', watchdog
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"The prison service, the police and
OL,8,Fother security services must urgently
OL,9,Fconfront organised gang activity and
OL,10,Freduce the supply of drugs and other
OL,11,Fillicit items which so clearly
OL,12,Fundermine every aspect of prison life."
OL,14,FShadow Justice Secretary Robert
OL,15,FJenrick raised the issue in Parliament
OL,16,Fon Tuesday, accusing Labour of
OL,17,Fallowing the problems with drone drops
OL,18,Fto "deteriorate".
