OL,11,Fgovernment, saying "we're taking
OL,12,Faction while they just spout."
OL,14,F"We are working hard to detect and
OL,15,Fdisrupt the use of drones", he said,
OL,16,Fbut couldn't go into detail about the
OL,17,Ftactics used given the "security
OL,18,Fimplications."
