OL,7,F"Drone sightings around prisons in
OL,8,FEngland and Wales are a matter of
OL,9,Fgreat concern, and pose a major threat
OL,10,Fto prison security", Dakin told the
OL,11,FCommons.
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Justice (MoJ) promised
OL,14,Fimprovements including a crackdown on
OL,15,Fdrugs after Taylor found there to be
OL,16,F"catastrophic levels" present at the
OL,17,Fcategory B prison in Manchester which
OL,18,Fcan hold more than 700 men, including
OL,19,Fa handful of the "most disruptive" and
OL,20,Fhigh-risk prisoners under close
OL,21,Fsupervision.
